00:11:20.960 --> 00:11:24.120
Atas perintahku, Akshay dan
anak-anak berpura-pura pingsan.

00:11:26.200 --> 00:11:27.720
'Dia pergi.'

00:11:35.160 --> 00:11:36.360
Aku sudah bilang pada mereka

00:11:36.680 --> 00:11:38.720
